  "description": {
    "collection": "JUVENTUS STORE ",
    "intro": "Stand with La Vecchia Signora as they set their sights on a return to the top of Serie A in the adidas Juventus 26/27 Authentic Home Shirt in White/Black, a high-performance home jersey dripping with Piedmontese pride.\r\n\r\nWorn by Kenan Yildiz, Jonathan David, Khephren Thuram, Lloyd Kelly, Bremer and the rest of the first-team squad at the pinnacle of the club game, the 2026/27 home shirt shows your undying support for the Bianconeri as they compete for a record-extending 37th Serie A title and aim for European glory. Returning to tradition, the classic black and white stripes are elevated with elegant gold detailing and a classy fold-over polo collar to create a tasteful, minimalist look befitting the most successful side in Italy, and the legendary Juve crest emblazoned over your heart displays your club pride for the world to see.\r\n\r\nNew Climacool+ technology utilises 3D body mapping and strategically placed ventilation to promote airflow and offer superb breathability that keeps you cool no matter how hard you push on the pitch, and mechanical stretch fabric delivers full freedom of movement for unrestricted performance. Moisture-wicking properties draw sweat away from the skin to ensure that you stay dry and comfortable while you compete in elite competitive matches, hone your body and skills in intense training sessions, and push the team on to greatness from the Juventus Stadium stands.\r\n\r\nMade from 100% recycled polyester, this shirt is perfect for the environmentally conscious Juve fan looking to make a difference.",
